{
  "stem": "2966.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- did have an inkling of what was happening because, in 1938, Hitler chased out all the Polish Jews that did not become citizens in Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these people slowly came back to their families, and they were telling us stories of what's happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, till 1939, things were bad for the Jews, but there weren't-- there were no actual killings or burning and crematorium or concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even some Jews, when they got in to the first camp-- I think was Dachau-- and some of them were arrested and then released later.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it wasn't as bad as it started in 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was two years older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was born on January 1st, 1923.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And she went also to public school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, I should mention, that we had-- our public schools were separate for boys and for girls, even though they were adjoining buildings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that, she went to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was a little older, so she was going out already with boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not quite-- our youth was not quite as advanced as youth-- young people here today, because a girl of 12, 13 years old was still a child.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, when the war broke out, my sister [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had very difficult times.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was a housekeeper, like most of the women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know of anybody that worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she kept the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had to cook and bake for Seder or Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She used to bake cakes and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and every day, my mother used to go to the market to buy fresh-- everything fresh, because there was no refrigeration.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
